	(107, 'R&F Design Engineer', 'Park Control & Communication', '', 'Full-time', 'Bangalore', 'On-site', NULL, '2-4 years', '"Designing"', 'The role requires strong expertise in RF system design, including transmitters, receivers, and antennas; proficiency with RF simulation tools like ADS, HFSS, or CST; and hands-on experience using spectrum and network analyzers. Candidates must understand telemetry protocols, wireless communication standards, modulation techniques, and EMI/EMC compliance. A Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Electrical or Electronics Engineering and 2–4 years of relevant RF design experience are mandatory.', NULL, '2026-02-05 09:27:52.658771+00', true, '2025-12-05 07:46:13.79744+00', '2026-01-06 09:27:52.658771+00', 'Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Electrical or Electronics Engineering', 'Senior', 500000, 500000, 'open', '2025-12-05 07:46:14.222+00', NULL, '["The role requires strong expertise in RF system design, including transmitters, receivers, and antennas; proficiency with RF simulation tools like ADS, HFSS, or CST; and hands-on experience using spectrum and network analyzers. Candidates must understand telemetry protocols, wireless communication standards, modulation techniques, and EMI/EMC compliance. A Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Electrical or Electronics Engineering and 2–4 years of relevant RF design experience are mandatory."]', '[]', '""', 0, 0, 0, '902d03ef-71c0-4781-8e09-c2ef46511cbb', 'R&F Design Engineer', '902d03ef-71c0-4781-8e09-c2ef46511cbb', '[-0.009905821,-0.0014617965,0.0038321998,-0.059526645,-0.036619436,0.0004543034,0.0031786908,0.008438292,-0.03107034,0.007630004,0.0015492176,0.007165669,-0.024764553,-0.011980998,0.08075996,-0.017644743,-0.009326834,-0.020453686,-0.010771434,0.05209728,0.015431984,0.0067987866,0.027080497,-0.0129325995,0.024993854,-0.022483002,-0.014629429,0.058059115,-0.00023395909,-0.010845956,0.04388829,-0.024695762,-0.035128977,-0.03556465,-0.027057566,0.018103346,0.03918761,-0.015638355,-0.026255