	(110, 'TL-.NET (C#.NET , WPF)', 'NEC Software Solutions', '', 'Full-time', 'Mumbai', 'On-site', NULL, '12 years+', '"Team Leader"', 'NEC Software Solutions is seeking an experienced Team Leader for .NET development. You will lead a team of developers working on enterprise applications using C#.NET and WPF. Responsibilities include technical leadership, code reviews, architecture decisions, mentoring junior developers, and ensuring delivery of high-quality software solutions. Strong experience with Microsoft technologies and team management skills required.', NULL, '2026-02-05 09:27:52.658771+00', true, '2025-12-05 07:55:26.389882+00', '2026-01-07 04:57:43.928625+00', 'Engineering Degree', 'Mid', 3000000, 3000000, 'open', '2025-12-05 07:55:26.753+00', NULL, '["•\tMinimum 10+ years’ experience developing software for enterprise applications / solutions, with the following:", "o\tC# with .NET Framework 4.8 / .NET 8.0", "o\tMicrosoft SQL Server", "o\tObject Oriented design and development", "o\tDeveloping high-performing, multi-threaded, real-time software", "o\tWindows System Services", "o\tRESTful APIs, web services", "o\tUnit testing, mock framework libraries such as Moq, dependency injection", "o\tSource code version control (Git, TFS)", "o\tMicrosoft Visual Studio and Microsoft Azure DevOps", "o\tContinuous integration (CI) and continuous deployment (CD)"]', '[]', '""', 0, 0, 0, '902d03ef-71c0-4781-8e09-c2ef46511cbb', 'TL-.NET (C#.NET , WPF)', '902d03ef-71c0-4781-8e09-c2ef46511cbb', '[-0.06265304,0.033609726,0.06957631,-0.020315593,-0.0009582393,-0.0100964205,-0.0008009622,0.06599192,-0.07168765,0.032333095,0.01689079,-0.047824502,-0.026121803,0.006438386,0.053814843,0.029730735,0.01709947,0.004600162,0.0094028665,0.044976637,0.027864892,0.025029302,0.008764552,0.015417756,0.038372535,0.009918429,-0.00038686322,0.020978458,-0.001686317,-0.010820663,0.05160529,-0.00671458,0.022205988,0.038102478,0.029288827,0.020511998,0.080771364,0.021052111,0.016804863,0.00770274